The bar is gonna be warm wood.

1068
01:11:32,696 --> 01:11:36,689
I just purchased a restaurant
from Laguna Beach -

1069
01:11:36,856 --> 01:11:39,416
with some buddies.

1070
01:11:39,576 --> 01:11:44,491
It will be a nice bonus.

1071
01:11:44,896 --> 01:11:47,808
We are currently renovating.

1072
01:11:48,416 --> 01:11:55,925
I want to be in
real estate business.

1073
01:11:56,096 --> 01:12:03,047
I would also like to be
in some kind of car business.

1074
01:12:03,216 --> 01:12:09,086
I also want to play through
America's top 100 golf courses.

1075
01:12:09,256 --> 01:12:11,212
It will probably take several years.

1076
01:12:11,616 --> 01:12:15,734
Ducks let me decide for myself
what I want to do.

1077
01:12:16,056 --> 01:12:20,607
I don't want a job
where I have to travel a lot.

1078
01:12:20,776 --> 01:12:23,336
That's why I won't become a coach.

1079
01:12:24,456 --> 01:12:28,335
I'll have many hobbies
and other things to do -

1080
01:12:28,536 --> 01:12:33,291
but I don't think I can find
the same passion for something else -

1081
01:12:33,456 --> 01:12:35,128
than I have for hockey.

1082
01:12:36,736 --> 01:12:39,455
Teemu is strapped in
and ready to go.

1083
01:12:41,216 --> 01:12:42,968
Ready? Now.

1084
01:12:48,256 --> 01:12:50,531
7.3 g! Great job!

1085
01:12:50,856 --> 01:12:53,768
My father has always had a lot of toys.

1086
01:12:54,296 --> 01:12:56,491
It came perhaps from there.

1087
01:12:56,736 --> 01:12:59,409
Cars have always been a
very important hobby for me.

1088
01:12:59,576 --> 01:13:02,374
My first car was a
big old American one.

1089
01:13:02,536 --> 01:13:07,405
He bought this '61 Lincoln
when he got a professional contract.

1090
01:13:07,736 --> 01:13:10,773
They've accumulated since then.

1091
01:13:11,056 --> 01:13:15,015
If I get a good offer,
I buy the car.

1092
01:13:15,216 --> 01:13:17,013
It was a fun meeting.

1093
01:13:17,176 --> 01:13:20,486
Jari Kurri, Teppo Numminen
and Teemu were there.

1094
01:13:20,896 --> 01:13:22,614
We went to eat hamburgers.

1095
01:13:23,056 --> 01:13:26,731
They ordered classic cars
before they ordered burgers.

1096
01:13:26,896 --> 01:13:29,774
It was easier to choose a car
than a burger.

1097
01:13:29,976 --> 01:13:32,444
Teemu drove here a lot.

1098
01:13:32,616 --> 01:13:36,052
He trained at drifting and stuff.

1099
01:13:36,536 --> 01:13:39,687
We drove around in the evenings.

1100
01:13:40,776 --> 01:13:43,415
It was great to drive in the evenings -

1101
01:13:43,616 --> 01:13:45,925
because you saw if someone came.

1102
01:13:46,416 --> 01:13:48,327
It was safer that way.

1103
01:13:48,576 --> 01:13:53,889
We have been cautious
not to do anything stupid.

1104
01:13:54,216 --> 01:13:59,495
I removed
driver's seat backrest -

1105
01:13:59,736 --> 01:14:03,331
so I could sit back
because I had plaster on my leg.

1106
01:14:04,416 --> 01:14:09,092
I used my crutch
for gas

1107
01:14:09,776 --> 01:14:13,132
and my right foot for the clutch.

1108
01:14:13,496 --> 01:14:18,570
We drove off to a
snow-filled ditch.

1109
01:14:19,176 --> 01:14:22,373
I couldn't push the car back to the road -

1110
01:14:22,536 --> 01:14:24,333
and neither could Sirpa.

1111
01:14:24,496 --> 01:14:27,488
We called our friend Jorkka
who fetched us.

1112
01:14:27,656 --> 01:14:31,410
I told him that
Sirpa had driven into the ditch.

1113
01:14:31,576 --> 01:14:35,967
It took him a year to get
that I had been driving.

1114
01:14:36,136 --> 01:14:38,445
If you watch him
for a day or two -

1115
01:14:38,616 --> 01:14:41,608
you will see that he is
completely insane.

1116
01:14:42,256 --> 01:14:45,771
The roads are better
and the rain ended.

1117
01:14:45,936 --> 01:14:47,654
Now I've got a race feeling.

1118
01:14:47,816 --> 01:14:51,604
One of my best friends,
Kaide Eklund, began rallying.

1119
01:14:52,336 --> 01:14:56,375
I sat in the car
a few times in training.

1120
01:14:56,776 --> 01:14:58,846
It was awesome.

1121
01:14:59,176 --> 01:15:01,815
Our contracts forbid
this kind of stuff.

1122
01:15:01,976 --> 01:15:06,367
There is a three page  list of
forbidden things.

1123
01:15:06,936 --> 01:15:13,205
So I competed under a false name,
Teukka Salama.

1124
01:15:13,536 --> 01:15:17,814
My first car was a Ford Escort RS2000
.

1125
01:15:18,176 --> 01:15:23,853
Next year I rented a
Mitsubishi Galant for a race.

1126
01:15:24,016 --> 01:15:27,247
Then we bought a
Mitsubishi Lancer Group N -

1127
01:15:27,416 --> 01:15:30,965
and in Jyväskylä, we finished a
race for the first time.

1128
01:15:31,136 --> 01:15:36,449
Then Marcus Grönholm gave
us his Toyota Corolla WRC.

1129
01:15:36,616 --> 01:15:38,971
We could run it at 200 km / h
in Ouninpohja.

1130
01:15:40,136 --> 01:15:43,606
I drove up the hill
and only saw the sky behind it.

1131
01:15:43,776 --> 01:15:46,529
The co-driver said "slow down" -

1132
01:15:46,776 --> 01:15:50,815
which I did,
but we still flew high.

1133
01:15:50,976 --> 01:15:55,367
The front wheels hit the ground first
and the back end just bounced.

1134
01:15:55,536 --> 01:15:57,811
We drove on the front wheels
for 10 to15 meters.

1135
01:15:57,976 --> 01:16:01,366
Luckily, I had the wheels straight.
Otherwise we would have been in the ditch.

1136
01:16:01,616 --> 01:16:05,768
The public prosecutor may bring charges
against Teemu Selanne for his car accident.

1137
01:16:06,136 --> 01:16:11,051
Kalervo Kummola loves rally
and has often been a co-driver.

1138
01:16:11,216 --> 01:16:14,652
It is our common hobby.

1139
01:16:14,816 --> 01:16:18,934
Pekka Huolman called and told
that he would go and train -

1140
01:16:19,696 --> 01:16:22,688
on a closed road near lkaalinen.

1141
01:16:22,856 --> 01:16:27,134
Team Europe had
organized training days.

1142
01:16:27,296 --> 01:16:31,687
I asked if Raimo Helminen
and his son wanted to come.

1143
01:16:31,856 --> 01:16:35,053
There were five people in my car.

1144
01:16:35,536 --> 01:16:39,449
We were told to stop the
training after nine at night.

1145
01:16:39,616 --> 01:16:41,208
It was ten to nine.

1146
01:16:41,496 --> 01:16:43,293
I said we'll go now.

1147
01:16:43,456 --> 01:16:46,766
I wanted to drive the course
both ways once more.

1148
01:16:46,936 --> 01:16:51,248
He wanted to run first
so he didn't have to eat dust.

1149
01:16:51,776 --> 01:16:54,927
He would wait for us
before he turned back.

1150
01:16:56,296 --> 01:16:58,173
I had a friend with me.

1151
01:16:58,336 --> 01:17:04,127
We drove to the other end in the normal rally style.

1152
01:17:04,896 --> 01:17:08,286
I turned and started
to wait Kalervo.

1153
01:17:08,536 --> 01:17:11,369
It was three or four to nine -

1154
01:17:11,576 --> 01:17:13,692
so I thought that he probably won't come.

1155
01:17:13,856 --> 01:17:15,608
I was going to run slowly.

1156
01:17:15,776 --> 01:17:19,246
My friend said how good the traction was.

1157
01:17:19,496 --> 01:17:21,214
I showed him -

1158
01:17:21,376 --> 01:17:26,734
how good the grip was
and how powerful the brakes were.

1159
01:17:26,896 --> 01:17:29,968
Teemu was so enthusiastic -

1160
01:17:30,656 --> 01:17:35,207
that he forgot our agreement.

1161
01:17:35,456 --> 01:17:38,573
I totally forgot
that Kalervo was coming.

1162
01:17:38,856 --> 01:17:40,528
There was a small crest.

1163
01:17:40,696 --> 01:17:43,574
Normally I would have run
at approximately 150 km / h

1164
01:17:43,776 --> 01:17:46,927
It was the only place
for three kilometers -

1165
01:17:47,096 --> 01:17:50,406
where you could not see
the oncoming traffic.

1166
01:17:50,816 --> 01:17:55,412
The car jumps about 20 meters high there.

1167
01:17:55,776 --> 01:17:58,529
There are three jumps on the route.

1168
01:17:58,696 --> 01:18:04,054
I was under the biggest one
when Teemu came flying.

1169
01:18:04,216 --> 01:18:06,013
When the car took off -

1170
01:18:06,176 --> 01:18:08,610
I saw Kalervo's car 30 meters away.

1171
01:18:08,976 --> 01:18:10,807
The only thing I remember -

1172
01:18:10,976 --> 01:18:15,492
was a windshield with the text
"Toyota Corolla".

1173
01:18:15,776 --> 01:18:19,735
When we landed
there was nothing I could do.

1174
01:18:20,176 --> 01:18:25,887
I think I saved us
by turning the car sideways.

1175
01:18:26,496 --> 01:18:30,091
My car flipped over twice
and ended up in the woods.

1176
01:18:30,616 --> 01:18:32,846
Kalervos car stopped quickly -

1177
01:18:33,056 --> 01:18:35,172
but the blast was a lot
harder for them.

1178
01:18:35,336 --> 01:18:36,974
The car caught fire.

1179
01:18:37,256 --> 01:18:39,247
I had time to think:

1180
01:18:39,416 --> 01:18:42,772
"Did I survive the crash
to burn to death?"

1181
01:18:42,976 --> 01:18:47,015
I jumped out to
check out Kalervo's car.

1182
01:18:47,216 --> 01:18:49,013
There were five people in it.

1183
01:18:49,176 --> 01:18:51,815
Everyone seemed relatively okay.

1184
01:18:52,696 --> 01:18:55,369
Everyone was in shock.

1185
01:18:55,576 --> 01:19:00,491
I lost my heel
and broke my arms.

1186
01:19:01,336 --> 01:19:05,011
Raimo Helminen
got internal injuries.

1187
01:19:05,616 --> 01:19:07,846
The recovery took all winter.

1188
01:19:08,936 --> 01:19:11,496
My brother-in-law broke his knee.

1189
01:19:11,656 --> 01:19:17,492
I realized what I had done
and collapsed on the ground.

1190
01:19:18,976 --> 01:19:20,728
I nearly fainted.

1191
01:19:20,896 --> 01:19:23,774
Teemu also contacted the Heavenly Father then.

1192
01:19:24,056 --> 01:19:28,811
We had a guardian angel
because nothing worse happened.

1193
01:19:29,536 --> 01:19:33,973
Given the circumstances,
we got off pretty lightly.

1194
01:19:34,416 --> 01:19:38,773
I was in a wheelchair for 3 1/2 months.

1195
01:19:39,616 --> 01:19:45,009
I had nightmares and woke
up sweating long afterwards.

1196
01:19:45,336 --> 01:19:47,406
Everything was my fault.

1197
01:19:47,656 --> 01:19:49,931
I drove, it was my responsibility.

1198
01:19:50,336 --> 01:19:53,089
After that, I didn't want
to go rallying again.

1199
01:20:01,456 --> 01:20:05,210
One day when I was a rookie
I went to our physiotherapist.

1200
01:20:06,256 --> 01:20:09,726
I said I was in little pain
and asked what we should do.

1201
01:20:09,896 --> 01:20:11,568
He was having a bad day.

1202
01:20:11,816 --> 01:20:16,014
He ​​had already received a couple of guys -

1203
01:20:16,176 --> 01:20:18,326
complaining about their problems.

1204
01:20:18,496 --> 01:20:22,091
He was annoyed and took me
a little farther away. He said:

1205
01:20:22,256 --> 01:20:24,531
"Fucking rookie -

1206
01:20:24,896 --> 01:20:29,447
First thing you have to learn in this
league is playing with the pain!"

1207
01:20:29,616 --> 01:20:31,208
I was like this...

1208
01:20:31,376 --> 01:20:35,210
I once took a puck here
and it broke in three places.

1209
01:20:35,536 --> 01:20:37,686
I still have three metal plates.

1210
01:20:37,856 --> 01:20:41,405
Here I got a fracture.
It was hit by a slap shot.

1211
01:20:41,696 --> 01:20:44,688
I broke the tibia and fibula
simultaneously.

1212
01:20:44,856 --> 01:20:47,245
Once I tore my Achilles tendon.

1213
01:20:47,456 --> 01:20:49,686
Here I had two fractures.

1214
01:20:49,856 --> 01:20:54,088
My left knee has been operated
on six or seven times.

1215
01:20:54,256 --> 01:20:58,249
The first thing I'll do
after quitting playing -

1216
01:20:58,976 --> 01:21:02,855
is having a knee surgery.
I'll get a prosthesis.

1217
01:21:03,176 --> 01:21:06,407
The tibia will be sort of  cut off -

1218
01:21:06,736 --> 01:21:10,775
and this turned
ten degrees outside.

1219
01:21:11,216 --> 01:21:13,605
The bones will be aligned again.

